Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.21,0:00:20.55,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,只能看見痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.38,0:00:27.02,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,只是空虛地渡過每一日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.69,0:00:33.63,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在充滿消沉心情的城市裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.26,0:00:39.93,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你在優美地閃耀着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.37,0:00:42.06,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't Stop！ Carry On！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.60,0:00:46.34,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,不要灰心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.81,0:00:48.78,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't Stop！ Shinin Oh！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.28,0:00:52.87,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,不要被破壞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.48,0:01:00.05,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,變成愛啊，像把宇宙包裏一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.46,0:01:05.48,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在抱緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.66,0:01:12.26,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在抱緊

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.94,0:01:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！後面呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.82,0:01:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索媽媽身亡這件事很殘酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.19,0:01:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他們知道了戰爭已完結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.70,0:01:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒戰鬥的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.80,0:01:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對人來說本來是最好的，\N但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.81,0:01:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逆襲的仙勒度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.40,0:02:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是農作物的貨倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.00,0:02:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那大細機動戰士也能蔵起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.58,0:02:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然簽定了停戰協定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.32,0:02:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但卑斯柏的\N機動戰士還在活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是甚麽回事呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.99,0:02:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪貝德小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.52,0:02:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫托拉度艦隊的\N主力已回去宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.66,0:02:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使我們看到敵人還在活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.63,0:02:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不能先動手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.13,0:02:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.60,0:02:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不能饒恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺死媽媽的莫托拉度艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的心情我好明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.74,0:02:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你為了\N你個人仇怨而戰的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.34,0:03:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 就不能讓你駕駛V高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.74,0:03:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒想過甚麽報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.21,0:03:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但敵人還在活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.02,0:03:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以戰鬥看來還要繼續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.58,0:03:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索，你聼到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！有好消息呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.32,0:03:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聼到嗎？你聼住呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.39,0:03:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們入假了，能回去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.79,0:03:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還給我呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.93,0:03:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！我們能回去\N卡沙尼里亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.83,0:03:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡沙尼里亞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.27,0:03:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哥美斯艦長讓我們放假吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.74,0:03:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是停戰協定被遵守的証據啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽的遺骨能葬在故鄉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.31,0:03:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，真的沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.61,0:03:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會嘗試叫\N哥美斯艦長也讓我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.79,0:03:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向大西洋前進嗎，\N白色機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.18,0:04:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！動吧！\N再過左面一點！左面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.59,0:04:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用機動戰士的手…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.39,0:04:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西西莉軍曹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使不習慣在重力下工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.33,0:04:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但實在太慢了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會在起航前完成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要習慣地球啊 知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴洛瑪中尉回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.77,0:04:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.61,0:04:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴洛瑪中尉降落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.18,0:04:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體各就各位！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.72,0:04:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的檢查怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.48,0:04:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西西莉，還未完成嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.66,0:04:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那部白色機動戰士\N一定要消滅啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.93,0:05:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然，本國想拖延時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才簽定停戰協定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.00,0:05:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我身為工程師覺得很羞恥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.10,0:05:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫托拉度艦隊本來的目的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.54,0:05:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球淨化作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.74,0:05:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊古少校不是一個\N半途而廢的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.11,0:05:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才繼續戰鬥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.51,0:05:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作要快點完成 知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能釣到甚麽呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們為何那麽開心呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.87,0:05:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪露天娜，別停手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.94,0:05:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，瑪露天娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.17,0:05:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能回去久別的故鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麽開心也不出奇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.31,0:05:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些也拜託你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.91,0:05:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麽多！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.05,0:05:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很倦了啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.78,0:05:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些重力下的工作！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有假放不好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.19,0:06:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！可以開動高達嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.89,0:06:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開動高達？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.56,0:06:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是要你幫手釣魚吧，\N去幫他們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.46,0:06:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,釣魚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.00,0:06:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然要費多些時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.50,0:06:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不可以提升高度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.03,0:06:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何不進入市内\N而要轉向北呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.17,0:06:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想麻煩雅迪.直布羅陀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.57,0:06:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不想令那班孩子\N想起以前的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.91,0:06:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這個弧度吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.35,0:06:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.55,0:06:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能釣到甚麽呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.15,0:06:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,釣到這麽大的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.86,0:06:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能令胡索恢復精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，華倫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也來好好享受\N釣魚之樂啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.74,0:06:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！瑪露天娜小姐，\N你們也來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.97,0:06:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想去外面，\N有很大的鹽味啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.48,0:06:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機械和汽油的味道好得多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭鹽味！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.38,0:07:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒不舒服呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.29,0:07:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是生物腐爛的氣味嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是討厭的氣味呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.26,0:07:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，\N她們還未能適應地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.73,0:07:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙長大的人\N會有那種感覺嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.00,0:07:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能結婚呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.50,0:07:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.77,0:07:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能適應地球就會那樣吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連那樣你也想到！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.77,0:07:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想在地球生活呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.44,0:07:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊啊，\N因為瑪露天娜小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒當你是男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.08,0:07:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那樣說真過份！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒理由會那樣吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事會變成障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令相愛的戀人分開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得悲哀的嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙長大的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.02,0:07:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連這個海的氣味也討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.16,0:07:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊斯卡羅的人\N應該也是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.53,0:07:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但為何他們甚至殺死我媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.60,0:07:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也要來地球呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.49,0:08:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是甚麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.59,0:08:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.55,0:08:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛得很高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.36,0:08:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是飛彈！飛彈呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.99,0:08:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提升高度！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.19,0:08:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體進入作戰狀態！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從哪裡來的！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是敵人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.80,0:08:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！敵人在哪裡！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.94,0:08:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打開和連賀斯Jr\N通訊的回路！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.31,0:08:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！奧迪羅和湯馬殊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.88,0:08:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用機動戰士擊毀飛彈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.31,0:08:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人既然來了，\N只有一戰吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道嘛！\N不能離開白色方舟！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.59,0:08:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了！來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.99,0:08:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們這要做違反協定啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.20,0:08:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連賀斯追上來要半日時間！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.50,0:09:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會向朗特歷部隊\N要求援助！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.17,0:09:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要支持下去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.61,0:09:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後方有東西浮上水面！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.41,0:09:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是莫托拉度戰艦嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.84,0:09:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.24,0:09:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是列斯迪亞級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有戰艦出來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.79,0:09:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只得一艘！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.56,0:09:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在水上也能移動！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.57,0:09:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要浪費彈藥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.57,0:09:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那是白色傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先要消滅敵人母艦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.34,0:09:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無家可歸的機動戰士就不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.38,0:09:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的敵手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.95,0:09:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算攻擊白色方舟嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.89,0:09:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛車胎型\N機動戰士血脈 沸騰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓮達！西西莉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.69,0:09:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯！這種駕駛感覺很特別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.26,0:10:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能用自己整備的機體出戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.13,0:10:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得很光榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.60,0:10:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦向我們還擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.40,0:10:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的動作太快了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.84,0:10:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去\N會變成敵人的標靶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.04,0:10:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧邊羅和湯馬殊\N保護白色方舟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據 情況作為\N白色方舟的引擎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.82,0:10:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡是大氣層内！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.82,0:10:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盾牌被…！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.99,0:10:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點本領！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.87,0:10:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中呀！給我中呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.80,0:10:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我沉吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.68,0:10:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎室中彈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.04,0:10:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是擦過罷了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.28,0:10:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫全體人員去滅火！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.98,0:10:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎！瑪露天娜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在滅火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.82,0:10:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米加粒子砲還能發射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.45,0:10:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.92,0:11:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還差一擊就能令敵艦沉沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.86,0:11:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.36,0:11:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色方舟後退了！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.03,0:11:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.70,0:11:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它不會沉沒，\N應該會停在島上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.98,0:11:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.28,0:11:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再噴多些滅火劑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.81,0:11:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.38,0:11:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒事了  真好彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.19,0:11:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎蒂！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.86,0:11:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…沒事！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你，瑪露天娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.88,0:11:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒跌下去真好彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.18,0:11:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭達斯，多謝\N，不用咬住我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎蒂！你流血呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.52,0:12:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擦傷罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.92,0:12:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是島呀，停在島上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.93,0:12:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停在海岸嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.66,0:12:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把白色方舟當為砲台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.53,0:12:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但沒有作為擋箭牌的岩石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湯馬殊！要降落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.20,0:12:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湯馬殊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,降落後，我們也能戰鬥了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.01,0:12:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方降落沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好臭呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.68,0:12:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！這些白色\N的是甚麽呀！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.12,0:12:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是鯨魚或其他魚骨吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.19,0:12:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉的腐爛氣味很臭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.39,0:12:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎蒂，好難受呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.39,0:12:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無…無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.29,0:12:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麽多白骨被沖上岸即是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.16,0:12:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個海被污染的\N程度還很嚴重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.80,0:12:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想一直留在這裡呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.67,0:12:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.34,0:12:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真過份！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屍體在悲哀海洋被污染嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.54,0:13:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屍體害怕腐爛變成白骨嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.91,0:13:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哪一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.18,0:13:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色方舟打算成為砲台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.35,0:13:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魚群循季節移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.82,0:13:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡死去而聚骨成山嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.62,0:13:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你們\N再污染地球的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.09,0:13:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要令敵人發現\N白色方舟的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.80,0:13:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.03,0:13:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.27,0:13:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫艾莉莎小姐\N等人出去外面！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.80,0:13:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎辦？爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.27,0:13:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照做！\N朗特歷部隊正趕來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.11,0:13:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,華倫，趁現在補給飛彈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.01,0:13:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在補給啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.78,0:13:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡死去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.48,0:13:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會像海岸的鯨魚\N和其他魚一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.68,0:13:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腐爛之後變成白骨！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.68,0:13:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發出這樣臭的氣味啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.59,0:13:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死在這裡呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.49,0:13:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽我也是\N初次看見這種情景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三號機，你太慢了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.63,0:14:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不來就不會死啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.21,0:14:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索擊潰了敵人的組合！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.38,0:14:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許會有大浪衝上來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後面沒事吧！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老鼠走進死胡同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令敵艦出來然後\N一口氣消滅它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.21,0:14:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！白色傢伙很利害！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.48,0:14:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，它配做我們的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.52,0:14:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然機動戰士退後了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.55,0:14:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那艘莫托拉度戰艦\N一定會來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.99,0:14:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V2的下身部份看來沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.66,0:15:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在爸爸他們正在檢查引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.53,0:15:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎交給你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道，武器方面怎樣呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.07,0:15:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會叫湯馬殊他們去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.90,0:15:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基利先生，我要運上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.91,0:15:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.24,0:15:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的地球\N沒理由能居住啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.84,0:15:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就哭個不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.98,0:15:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能戰鬥的人\N就離開這艘船吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.71,0:15:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別那樣說啊，\N看到這種情景嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死後腐爛是當然的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.75,0:15:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,華倫講得無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.52,0:15:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎蒂！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們和鯨魚是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.06,0:15:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受傷後就一樣會流血吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死後就會腐爛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.53,0:15:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你流血呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然啊，我受了傷嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.17,0:15:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是！海岸上的\N白骨很恐怖啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.87,0:15:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是因為\N這個地球的環境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.11,0:15:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得令動物不能安祥地死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.74,0:15:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力生存的話就能死得安祥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.08,0:15:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在已變得不能夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.98,0:15:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力生存就能\N死得安祥了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.22,0:15:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是那樣想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.82,0:15:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但因為現在的地球不是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.05,0:16:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們一定要為了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.76,0:16:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,創造一個能活得\N美好的環境而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道那樣戰鬥\N就是為了…！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.73,0:16:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了活得美好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.66,0:16:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這很痛苦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.37,0:16:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，胡索也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使他媽媽的遺體變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.14,0:16:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也在戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.61,0:16:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索的媽媽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.51,0:16:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活得美好即是\N努力生存的意思嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.74,0:16:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.81,0:16:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是發抖，\N會在這裡腐爛而死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.28,0:16:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪露天娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.45,0:16:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在有生之年盡\N自己所能去做事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.75,0:16:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就能死得安祥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.43,0:16:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車胎型機動戰士\N不要飛上天空！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.76,0:16:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用車胎去消滅\N遊擊隊的戰艦和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.66,0:16:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.87,0:16:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人戰機接近！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.07,0:16:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,張開彈幕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.60,0:16:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓮達！西西莉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒼蠅就交給你們消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.07,0:16:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本艦向小島進發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何不肯停止攻擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.95,0:17:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然那樣唯有一戰！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從低空攻擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.92,0:17:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.32,0:17:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！白色傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.09,0:17:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防守很堅固！\N攻擊白色方舟！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.40,0:17:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅！湯馬殊！\N從左右過去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.11,0:17:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不成為他們的障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.67,0:17:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是我們的任務啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.28,0:17:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.22,0:17:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家不要死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.02,0:17:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二輪攻擊來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.02,0:17:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你們成功的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.99,0:17:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要擋住它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.96,0:17:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用水柱做擋箭牌？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.37,0:17:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也用！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.60,0:17:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也用水柱嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.37,0:18:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.58,0:18:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！白色傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.71,0:18:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的口很可怕呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.32,0:18:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.92,0:18:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓮達中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.76,0:18:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次！  知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.16,0:18:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.56,0:18:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西西莉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.60,0:18:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人在\N那種地方有援軍嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.98,0:18:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,張開彈幕！敵人援軍來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.35,0:18:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有聯邦軍在北海嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.91,0:18:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是神聖軍事同盟嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.09,0:18:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朗特歷部隊來到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.59,0:18:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是聯邦軍！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.49,0:18:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.60,0:18:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓這艘船做我的腳部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.73,0:18:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道，別被抛下來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.67,0:19:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又那樣使用！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.58,0:19:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪貝德小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.22,0:19:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主砲被擊毀！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又多一部！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.63,0:19:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我進行接近戰吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.20,0:19:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.57,0:19:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！白色傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.14,0:19:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們連主砲也不能用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢殺死我的同伴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.68,0:19:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.02,0:19:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快離開戰線！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.35,0:19:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做不到！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.42,0:19:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主砲被擊毀，\N聯邦軍的援軍來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.76,0:19:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我方很不利呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.87,0:20:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.41,0:20:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再接近些就危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.08,0:20:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些就是\N朗特歷部隊的船嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.22,0:20:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救了我們的就是那些船嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.65,0:20:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哥美斯艦長\N以前所屬的部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.63,0:20:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有協助\N神聖軍事同盟的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.66,0:20:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然找了你們很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.00,0:20:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你們也很了得呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.83,0:20:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩部布拉斯達的\N機師也是少年吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.60,0:20:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了，\N下次不用哥美斯開口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.67,0:20:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也會來幫手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.91,0:20:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.14,0:20:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麽，我們去附近戒備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.08,0:20:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.49,0:21:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種火竟然這麽溫暖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.09,0:21:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯，這種溫暖\N的感覺很舒服呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.30,0:21:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.46,0:21:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.13,0:21:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.50,0:21:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅你也是那樣想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.04,0:21:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.24,0:21:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.54,0:21:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉莎和瑪露天娜也變得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.61,0:21:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不討厭這些氣味了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.25,0:21:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也說得無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.78,0:21:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是風浪令氣味消失了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.08,0:21:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.55,0:21:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那樣你們就能\N在地球生活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.69,0:21:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而華倫呢，就能結婚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅！飲多杯咖啡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.39,0:21:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不飲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.63,0:21:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麽事？華倫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.90,0:21:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.56,0:21:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們習慣了地球的氣味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.83,0:21:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很開心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.77,0:21:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使死亡是理所當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.71,0:22:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我能忘記\N憎恨和復仇的心嗎

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.38,0:22:36.85,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在銀色的海上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.25,0:22:41.52,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,灼熱的波浪湧上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.92,0:22:46.42,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,看到跪下的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.93,0:22:55.03,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有變成說話 只是你的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.44,0:23:00.63,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,能變得優美就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.17,0:23:03.90,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,再次TENDERNESS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.41,0:23:08.81,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你的内心在月亮的菱鏡上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.18,0:23:13.68,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,抱着閃耀的未來在跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.15,0:23:20.25,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能再次和你見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.69,0:23:26.43,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你的瞳孔顯出孤獨

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.97,0:23:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當歐洲就在眼前時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.01,0:23:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑斯柏又來攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.41,0:23:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅令大家捲入戰鬥中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.81,0:23:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想負責任而過度奮勇作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.72,0:23:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索把V2的盾牌開到最大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.45,0:23:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,企圖趕走莫托拉度戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.99,0:23:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回，機動戰士V高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.66,0:23:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北海滿佈火災
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請收看吧

